Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate Gary Greene -

data.description: Absolutely stunning one-story available in Woodwind Lakes. Completely updated home exuding elegance and style. 4 spacious bedrooms, 2 gorgeous bathrooms, both formals. A two-sided fireplace creates a cozy ambiance, seamlessly connecting the living spaces. The kitchen is a chef’s dream boasting an extended island, Subway tile backsplash, under cabinet lighting, stainless steel appliances, double ovens and a brick accent wall.  Fabulous primary suite complete with a spa-like bathroom featuring a dual granite vanity, whirlpool tub and frameless oversized shower. Additional features include wood flooring, crown molding, updated light fixtures throughout. Serene backyard retreat offers a relaxing hot tub and gazebo.  Perfect for outdoor entertaining or relaxing, peaceful evenings. Don't miss this opportunity to make this your forever home!  Zoned to highly acclaimed CFISD.
